"     April F Eichler, MD, MPH",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/16/18697/contributors\">",
"     Janet L Wilterdink, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
